    "name": "Bitas",
    "profile": "Sebastian Bedregal Belmont (Bitas) is a young DJ and Producer from La Paz, Bolivia. Who's been producing electronic music and playing on several events this 2017.\r\nHe started his musical career in 2014 releasing his first original piece, ‘Azimuth’ in March 13th of 2015 in Blow The Roof Records, then he released \"Hype Up\" on May 29th and ‘Resonation’ on September 8th. His track ‘T.I.K.I’ with Tegi was released on Brooklyn Fire Records.\r\nHis release ‘Whispers’ has reached Armada Music getting support out from big names.\r\nReleased Nocturne on the CELL Network's ADE Sampler 2016 and he had end up 2016 with Requiem, out now on the CELL Network.\r\nStarted 2017 with ‘Sphinx’ together with Jakik, out on CELL Recordings. His track ‘Galactic’ together with ANG and Syzz got played by BLASTERJAXX at Tomorrowland Brasil 2016, out on TNC Recordings.\r\nHis ‘The Twilight Faithful’ remix got massive support from Knife Party, out on BANG IT! Records. He released his ‘You’ remix on BANG IT Records! On Marc",
